featured_reviews.review_id:
Alhamdulillaah. Yeh Ek Aesi Masjid hai jis me Mard Hazraat ke Elaawa Parda ke Saath Auraton ke namaaz padhne ka bhi intezam hai, jo mere hisaab se Bahat hi achchhi baat hai Q K juma ke khutbo ke zariye Auraton ko bhi Sahi Deen seekhne ko milta hai, jo har Aurat ke liye bhi bahat hi zaroori hai.
Allaah Taala Masjid ke Intezamiya ko imaan-O-Sehat ke saath salamat rakkhe. Aameen

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Alhamdulillah. This is the only Masjid in which there is a provision for offering Namaz of Auraton behind the curtain behind Mard Hazraat, which according to me is a very good thing. Q. Through the Friday sermons, Auraton also gets the opportunity to learn the Sahi Deen, which is It is important for women too.
May Allah keep the members of Taala Masjid safe and sound. Aameen
